{"tid":609633,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★貿易戰嚇死Gay CooK ! 大叫：iPhone 是「美國製造」！","createTime":"2018-03-29T07:49:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-29T09:38:20.000Z","uid":19454,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"c118353f258079f17ba18c5f024afd45be29e58e","tid":609633,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T07:49:42.000Z","msg":"Tim Cook 在接受 Recode 網站和 MSNBC 的訪問時大爆金句：<span style=\"color: red;\">「我們在美國製造東西，iPhone 不是在美國製造的說法是錯的」</span>，他說用戶只是專注於組裝部分，才會有「中國製造」的錯覺，但事實上 iPhone 元件是從世界各國代工製造。Tim Cook 舉出一個例如就是 iPhone 螢幕玻璃，是在美國肯塔基州的康寧工場代工，iPhone X 的 Face ID 模組是在德克薩斯州的廠房生產，而美國更多廠房亦為蘋果製造不同種類的元件。因此無需任何政治壓力，其實蘋果早已增加投資美國創造職位。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/tim-cook-said-iphone-is-made-in-usa_00-696x390.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.newmobilelife.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F03%2Ftim-cook-said-iphone-is-made-in-usa_00-696x390.jpg&h=10134452&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.newmobilelife.com/2018/03/29/tim-cook-said-iphone-is-made-in-usa/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newmobilelife.com%2F2018%2F03%2F29%2Ftim-cook-said-iphone-is-made-in-usa%2F&d=WtV8rLE4pArhkj3eEZDXmQdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=07b90422\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.newmobilelife.com/2018/03/29/tim-cook-said-iphone-is-made-in-usa/</a>"},{"pid":"33f1a731b4e21481d99e99eb7e289dd8fa5992dd","tid":609633,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T07:49:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"710b70a5be9e016c2e3af3576c57c07562893cc1","tid":609633,"uid":19454,"like":1,"disli